So what happens when someone goes over the 3,000 allowed visits per month in the basic plan?
is this just 3,000 tracked visits a month or a hard stop of 3,000 visits
It's tracked at 3,000 visits -- your CSM/CAM will reach out if you exceed that and talk about moving up to the $300 version of the Website Add-on. It's not a hard stop at 3,000 visits though.
<@U22PU4G4A> so if someone is on the basic plan with a website add-on (not the website starter) then this is unlimited visitors correct?
Correct. Someone on the $300 Website Add-on has unlimited visits
Thank you for the verification Jeff:)
<@U22PU4G4A> one more quick follow up, is the tracked vistors unlimited as well whne buying the $300 website addon or is that capped by the marketing plan??
I believe it's capped by marketing plan -- but your CAM/CSM is probably the best resource there.
